.TH "libnvme_ns_copy_uuid" 9 "libnvme_ns_copy_uuid" "June 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_ns_copy_uuid \- Copy UUID of a namespace into a caller buffer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" libnvme_ns_copy_uuid
.BI "(libnvme_ns_t n "  ","
.BI "unsigned char out[NVME_UUID_LEN] "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "n" 12
Namespace instance
.IP "out" 12
buffer for the UUID
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Copies the namespace's uuid into \fIout\fP
